{
  "stem": "21437.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She needed to tell me that she knew all along.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On my body.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I wore always something that had a little pocket.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had something like a-- they used to have then-- you know when you wear pajamas, sort of like bands, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it sort of-- I sort of-- by that time, I was very adept, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew exactly how, and what, and when.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was not out of the ghetto, but it was something like-- it was a way there, where this man who was a Pole-- where this man and my father-- my father didn't-- he perhaps, he felt that the less I know the better.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't ask him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was not important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whatever my father said, I knew I trusted him 100%.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I knew that it had to be done this way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I knew it was between-- he said it was between you and me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, of course, this meant-- and nobody else knows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember any barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just remember that it was confined to a few streets and that my whole life revolved going in the morning to [NON-ENGLISH], coming back.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had just this way-- getting up in the morning, going for the bread, going to lessons, coming back, reading something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If there were something to eat, eating something, going again to lessons, coming back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is really-- you know-- the rest, it's sort of-- at that time, this time, in the ghetto, somehow it was-- where the details somehow are not engraved, you know, in my mind.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It is just-- things had to be done.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You went, and you did it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you sort of-- it was-- it was a struggle from second to second.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
